APPROVAL NOTIFICATION Please do not reply to this message. If you need assistance or have questions, please contact your local representative

Dear Approver,


This mail is sent to you to notify Order {!Order.OrderNumber} needs your approval :


- End Customer Company : {!Order.NATT_End_Customer__c}
- Account name : {!Order.NATT_Account_Name__c}
- Opportunity name : {!Order.Opportunity}
- Quote Number : {!Order.Quote}
- Amount : {!Order.TotalAmount}
- Purchase Order Number: {!Order.NATT_Purchase_Order__c}


Cancellation Reason: {!Order.Cancellation_Reason__c}


Direct link to Order: {!Order.Order_Link__c}

Thank you!
